description:
Introducing the newest Audioboom original podcast, Here's the Sitch with Mike & Laurens. hosted by The Jersey Shore's Mike 'The Situation' Sorrentino and his wife Lauren. Join 'The Situation' as he talks about his path to recovery, going back to work and everything else in between. Here's the Sitch with Mike and Laurens premieres 3/3. Subscribe to Here's the Sitch with Mike and Laurens on Apple Podcasts: https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/heres-the-sitch-with-mike-laurens/id1499164128
